    <h2>From crowded cubicle to 2-level office</h2>
    <h3>As our company has grown, so has our impact on the planet</h3>

    <div class="large-text space-bottom">
        
        <p>
            OPOWER signed its first utility client in 2007 from a rented desk in a San Francisco cubicle pit. Since then, the company has grown to a $30mm business, with 37 utility clients and a product that will soon reach more than 5 million homes.         
        </p>
    
        <p>
            OPOWER is saving money, saving energy, reducing carbon emissions and helping to create jobs, and our impact is increasing every day. Interested in how this all came to be? Just keep reading.        
        </p>
    
    </div>
    
